From: MaSi-OS <masi@local>
Subject: [PATCH] misc: fastrpc: ADSP sensor PD routing + legacy ioctl (linux 7.0)

Adapted from Batocera Custom Qualcomm Builds (suckbluefrog) for AYN Thor/Odin2
gyro via ADSP SensorsPD. Uses dma_addr (linux 7.0) instead of downstream phys.

